; 各種クエストシナリオ（体験版搭載分）




;■牢獄クエスト

; 牢獄に囚われた人たちを助け出すクエスト
; 助けに行くつもりが主人公たちが捕まってしまう

;◇イベント01・入口の罠
*jail_01

; ☆フリーモード
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*jail_01 cond='game.isFreeMode'

; 牢獄入口
@se f=kacha
@wait time=1000
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「...?!」[k]
[textoff]
@playse storage=acid
@image layer=e1 storage=9999 opacity=0 visible=true
@image layer=e2 storage=PE_base_full left=0 top=0 visible=true
@startemit layer=e2 storage=PE_smoke_gray time=2500
@move layer=e1 time=2000 path=,,255
@wait time=2000
[texton]
The moment we stepped on the floor of the passageway in front of the door, pure white smoke billowed out from the surrounding walls![k]
The narrow aisle quickly filled with smoke. As everyone inhaled it, they collapsed![k]
[テオ f=09]「Damn it... a trap...!」[k]
[textoff]
@black time=1000
@layopt layer=e1 visible=false
@clearemit layer=e2
@w2

[iscript]
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
o.マリア.exp = o.マリア.getNeedExp(20);	// マリアのレベルを上げておく
o.マリア.levelUpToTheLast();

f.allPrisoners = [
	"看守","看守"
	,"囚人","囚人","囚人","囚人"
	,"シスター","シスター","シスター","シスター","シスター"
];
f.atrociousPrisoners = ["バジリスク", "デザートバイパー", "マンイーター"];
f.atrociousPrisoners.shuffle();

f.partyPrisonerNums = [];
f.stolenWeapons = [];
for(var i = game.party.members.count - 1; i >= 0; i--)
{
	var one = game.party.members[i];
	if(one == game.playerChara) continue;
	if(one == o.マックス) continue;
	f.partyPrisonerNums.add(game.chara.find(one));
	game.party.removeMember(one);
	f.allPrisoners.add("仲間");
}

while(f.allPrisoners.count < 18) f.allPrisoners.add("なし");
f.allPrisoners.shuffle();
f.partyPrisonerNums.shuffle();
f.partyPrisonerNums.unshift(game.chara.find(o.マックス));
game.party.removeMember(o.マックス);

game.guest.eraseHiring();	// 召喚・雇用キャラを外す
for(var i = game.guest.members.count - 1; i >= 0; i--)
{
	game.removeMemberTemporary(game.guest.members[i]);
}
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[endscript]

; 牢屋に移動
@warp map=牢獄Ｂ２ x=7 y=5 way=s sound=false

; テオが収監された牢屋
@black off=0
[texton]
[テオ f=12][nw]「...Ah!」[/nw][k]
When I woke up, I was in a small stone room.[k]
Where... Could this be a prison?[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
How shameful... To be captured like this by the enemy...[k]
Is this how the criminals have been capturing adventurers who came to investigate? No wonder no one is coming back.[k]
I need to figure out a way to get out of here. I'm also worried about everyone in the party.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント02・マリアが救出に来る
*jail_02

; ☆フリーモード
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*jail_02 cond='game.isFreeMode'

; テオが収監された牢屋
@wait time=500
[texton]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I touch the door of the prison.[k]
The door is very sturdy, made of steel, and it is unlikely that it could be broken.[k]
The walls are made of stone and look solid, so it would take decades to even drill a hole in them.[k]
...The prison is unexpectedly strong. It may be almost impossible to escape by force.[k]
Was I destined to rot away as a prisoner...?[k]
@se f=kacha
∗click∗[k]
[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
Suddenly, with the sound of a key being turned, the door to the room opened slightly![k]
Why unlock it? What does the enemy want with me?[k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@walk move=n
[texton]
[テオ f=06]「...!」[k]
In any case, this is my chance! I must get out of here immediately.[k]
[textoff]
@se f=door4
@wait time=500
@fg c=マリア e=通常 f=05
[texton w=1]
[マリア v=va192 f=05]「Hey! Are you okay?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Maria!」[k]
To my surprise, it was that Maria who opened the door to the cell.[k]
Hey, why are you here?[k]
[マリア v=va194 f=05]「I'm here to help you. So get out while there are no guards nearby!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「O-oh...」[k]
[textoff]
@black on=500
@wait time=500
@warp x=6 y=3 way=w sound=false
@fgf c=マリア f=02
@black off=500
[texton]
[マリア v=va195 f=02]「Hey, that was a disaster.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「How did you know...? What's going on?」[k]
[マリア v=va196 f=14]「Well... Actually, the client for your quest is me.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Huh? What's going on?」[k]
[マリア v=va197 f=02]「...As I'm sure you've heard, this quest was attempted by several parties of adventurers. They all disappeared without being able to solve it.」[k]
[マリア v=va198 f=02]「The client was at a loss as to why.」[k]
[マリア v=va199 f=02]「So, I decided to find out why adventurers keep disappearing in this prison and then launch a full-scale rescue operation.」[k]
[テオ f=00]「...」[k]
[マリア v=va200 f=02]「I was consulted by the client about this matter before you guys.」[k]
[マリア v=va201 f=02]「After much deliberation, we decided to have someone else take on this request and observe how the enemy catches adventurers who try to infiltrate.」[k]
[マリア v=va202 f=02]「Then you guys took up the offer and I followed you to the prison.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「No way!」[k]
[マリア v=va203 f=02]「I watched from a distance as you infiltrated this prison.」[k]
[マリア v=va204 f=02]「After finding out about that immobilization trap at the entrance, I was able to sneak in without being caught by the enemy.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...So we were used as bait.」[k]
[マリア v=va205 f=53]「Sorry! But I was going to get you guys out of there right away and have you do the rescue mission with me! I'm pretty good at picking locks.」[k]
[テオ f=00]「...」[k]
I'm a little baffled, but it worked out anyway, so I guess that's good...[k]
[テオ f=05]「I get it. Then let's go help everyone else as soon as possible!」[k]
[マリア v=va206 f=10]「Hmmm... As much as I'd like to...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What's the problem?」[k]
[マリア v=va207 f=09]「The cell doors here are much sturdier than I thought they would be. It would take a long time to pry them open. Your cell happened to have a simple lock, so I was able to open it...」[k]
[マリア v=va208 f=09]「Given time I could pick the other ones, but if it's too slow, the guards would find out. I'd like to get the [b]prison key[/b] if possible. The guards should have it...」[k]
[テオ f=00]「Ok, I've got it. Let's get the key to the jail first!」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@eval exp='game.guest.entry(o.マリア)'
@st
@se f=up3
@notice text="<y>Maria joined the party!"
@mu f=&'game.map.bgm'
[eventoff]


;◇イベント03・牢屋の鍵を奪う
*jail_03

; 牢の並ぶ廊下
@fg l=kobold_white left=340 top=80 b
@fgf r=kobold_white left=560 top=80
[texton]
[name n=Guard]「What the hell! How did you get out of there?」[k]
[マリア v=va209 f=06]「This isn't good...」[k]
The guards have found us! We have to take them down before the other guards gather![k]
[textoff]
@clf

; 看守と戦闘
@monster pos=2 name=ウインターコボルド
@monster pos=4 name=ウインターコボルド
@callbattle escape=false
; 勝利

@treasure item=牢屋の鍵
[texton]
[マリア v=va210 f=01]「Lucky! These guys had the keys!」[k]
[マリア v=va211 f=02]「Things were a bit sketchy for a while, but we should be okay now. So, let's go get everyone out of there.」[k]
[textoff]
@delevent
[eventoff]




;◇イベント04・囚われた仲間の救出
*jail_04

@jump target=*_jail_04_prisoner cond='f.allPrisoners[0] == "囚人"'
@jump target=*_jail_04_keeper cond='f.allPrisoners[0] == "看守"'
@jump target=*_jail_04_sister cond='f.allPrisoners[0] == "シスター"'
@jump target=*_jail_04_nobody cond='f.allPrisoners[0] == "なし"'

; 仲間たちのいる牢屋に入る
@delevent
@eval exp='f.allPrisoners.shift()'
@eval exp='game.curChara = game.chara[f.partyPrisonerNums[0]]'
[if exp='! game.isFreeMode']
	@jump target=*_jail_04_max cond='game.curChara == o.マックス'
	@jump target=*_jail_04_last cond='f.partyPrisonerNums.count == 1'
[endif]
@jump target=*_jail_04_others

*_jail_04_prisoner
; 囚人とバトル
@monster pos=3 name=囚人
@callbattle
@delevent
@eval exp='f.allPrisoners.shift()'
[eventoff]

*_jail_04_keeper
; 看守とバトル
@wait time=1000
@fg l=kobold_white left=340 top=80 b
@fgf r=kobold_white left=560 top=80
[texton]
[name n=Guard]「What the hell! How did you get out of there?」[k]
[マリア v=va212 f=06]「This isn't good...」[k]
There happened to be a guard in the room. Now that it had come to this, we had no choice but to fight.[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@monster pos=2 name=ウインターコボルド
@monster pos=4 name=ウインターコボルド
@callbattle
@delevent
@eval exp='f.allPrisoners.shift()'
[eventoff]

*_jail_04_sister
; シスター救出
@wait time=1000
[texton]
@eval exp='f.temp = "priest_" + ["purple", "red", "green", "pink"].draw() + "_03"'
[name n=Sister f=&'f.temp']「Oh... You're... What?」[k]
[マリア v=va213 f=07]「We're here to help you! Now, get out of here as fast as you can!」[k]
[name n=Sister f=&'f.temp']「Oh, thank you!」[k]
[textoff]
@se f=period
@notice text="<y>One Sister rescued!"
@delevent
@eval exp='f.allPrisoners.shift()'
[eventoff]

*_jail_04_nobody
; 誰もいない
@wait time=1000
[texton]
[マリア v=va214 f=06]「There's no one here...」[k]
There doesn't seem to be anyone here. Let's look elsewhere.[k]
[textoff]
@delevent
@eval exp='f.allPrisoners.shift()'
[eventoff]

*_jail_04_max
; マックス救出
@wait time=1000
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Max!」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Yo, [テオ]! You're here to help!」[k]
@se f=period
@eval exp='game.party.entry(game.curChara)'
I found Max in the cell. He rejoined the group.[k]
[マックス f=21]「Oh, Maria! You came to save me, didn't you?!」[k]
[マリア v=va215 f=52]「Hi, long time no see, Max...」[k]
; ↑ 気まずそうに
[マックス f=92]「I can't believe you'd risk your life for me! I knew you- 」[k]
[マリア v=va216 f=27]「It's not like that! Don't get me wrong!」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Don't be shy! You really like me, don't you?」[k]
[マリア v=va217 f=27]「I told you it's not like that! Stay away from me!」[k]
[マックス f=33]「I love you too～ Now, kiss me!」[k]
[テオ f=07]「Max!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Hey, what the hell, [テオ]. Don't yell at me all of a sudden.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「We still need to find everyone else. Let's hurry up and go look for them!」[k]
[マックス f=95]「O-oh... Okay, okay... 」[k]
[textoff]
@eval exp='f.partyPrisonerNums.shift()'
[eventoff]

*_jail_04_others
; 仲間を１人救出
@wait time=1000
[texton]
[if exp='! game.isFreeMode']
	[テオ f=05]「[キャラ]! Are you safe?!」[k]
	[キャラ f=11]「Captain...!」[k]
[endif]
@se f=period
@eval exp='game.party.entry(game.curChara)'
[name key=&'game.curChara.keyName' f=01] [キャラ] was inside the cell. Now free, [キャラ] rejoined the party![k]
[textoff]
@eval exp='f.partyPrisonerNums.shift()'
[eventoff]

*_jail_04_last
; 最後の１人を救出
; 囚われた仲間の１人が看守にいたずらされている
@wait time=1000
[texton]
[name n=Guard f=orc_03]「Heh heh heh... Are you feeling good?」[k]

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh065 e=裸 f=37]「No... Don't... No...!」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve066 e=裸 f=37]「No... Don't... No...!」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd065 e=裸 f=37]「No... Don't... No...!」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg054 e=裸 f=37]「No... Don't... No...!」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs067 e=裸 f=37]「No... Don't... No...!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=05]「[キャラ]...!」[k]
[キャラ] was inside the cell. To my shock, her clothes had been removed, she'd been tied up, and a guard was relentlessly playing with her body![k]
This is terrible! We have to rescue her quickly...![k]
[テオ f=07]「Stop that! Get away from [キャラ]!」[k]

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh066 e=裸 f=31]「Captain...!」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve067 e=裸 f=31]「Captain...!」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd066 e=裸 f=31]「Captain...!」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg055 e=裸 f=31]「Captain...!」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs068 e=裸 f=31]「Captain...!」[k]
[endif]

@fg l=orc_green left=250 top=45 b
@fg c=orc_blue left=450 top=45 b
@fgf r=orc_green left=650 top=45
[name n=Guard f=orc_03]「What the hell?! How did you get in here?」[k]
[テオ f=07]「I won't forgive you if you lay a hand on an important member of my party!」[k]
[name n=Guard f=orc_02]「What the hell? You're with this woman?」[k]
[name n=Guard f=orc_03]「Fine! I'll take care of these guys first!」[k]
[textoff]
@clf

; 看守たちと戦闘
@monster pos=1 name=オークシャーマン
@monster pos=2 name=オークキング
@monster pos=3 name=オークキング
@monster pos=4 name=オークキング
@monster pos=5 name=オークシャーマン
@callbattle escape=false
; 勝利・救出

[texton]
@eval exp='game.curChara = game.chara[f.partyPrisonerNums[0]]'
[テオ f=05]「[キャラ], are you all right?」[k]

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh067 e=裸 f=25]「Y-yes...」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve068 e=裸 f=25]「Y-yes... 」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd067 e=裸 f=25]「Y-yes...」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg056 e=裸 f=25]「Y-yes...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs069 e=裸 f=25]「Y-yes... 」[k]
[endif]

@se f=period
@eval exp='game.party.entry(game.curChara)'
[キャラ] put her equipment back on and rejoined the group.[k]
[textoff]
@eval exp='f.partyPrisonerNums.shift()'
[eventoff]


;◇イベント05・逃げていた他の仲間と合流する
*jail_05

; ☆フリーモード
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*jail_05 cond='game.isFreeMode'

; 監獄の外
@wait time=500

; サンドラが仲間だった場合
[if exp='game.waitingMembers.has(o.サンドラ) || game.waitingMembers.has(o.ブルー)']
	@fg l=ブルー f=06 b
	@fg c=サンドラ f=05 b
	@fg r=ライナス f=06
	[texton w=1]
	[サンドラ v=vn038 f=05]「Oh, there you are. Honestly, I was so worried.」[k]
	When we walked out of the jail, Sandra, Blue, and Linus were waiting for us. Everyone seemed to be safe.[k]
	@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.マリア)'
	@eval exp='game.restoreMembers()'
	@clf
	@se f=period
	@notice text="<y>Blue, Sandra, and Linus rejoined the party!"
; ミレディが仲間だった場合
[elsif exp='game.waitingMembers.has(o.ミレディ)']
	@fg l=ミレディ f=01 b
	@fg r=ライナス f=06
	[texton w=1]
	[ミレディ v=vm182 f=01]「Ahh! There you are! You're safe～!」[k]
	When we walked out of the jail, Miredy and Linus were waiting for us, both of them seemingly safe.[k]
	@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.マリア)'
	@eval exp='game.restoreMembers()'
	@clf
	@se f=period
	@notice text="<y>Miredy and Linus rejoined the party!"
; ポラリスが仲間だった場合
[elsif exp='game.waitingMembers.has(o.ポラリス)']
	@fg l=ポラリス f=01 b
	@fg r=ライナス f=06
	[texton w=1]
	[ポラリス v=vp031 f=01]「We were very worried. I am glad to hear that everyone is safe.」[k]
	When we walked out of the jail, I found Lady Polaris and Linus waiting for us, both of them seemingly safe.[k]
	@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.マリア)'
	@eval exp='game.restoreMembers()'
	@clf
	@se f=period
	@notice text="<y>Polaris and Linus rejoined the party!"
; ライナスのみが仲間だった場合
[elsif exp='game.waitingMembers.has(o.ライナス)']
	@fg c=ライナス f=05
	[texton w=1]
	[ライナス f=06]「Yo.」[k]
	When we walked out of the jail, Linus was waiting for us. Apparently, he was safe.[k]
	@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.マリア)'
	@eval exp='game.restoreMembers()'
	@clf
	@se f=period
	@notice text="<y>Linus rejoined the party!"
[else]
	@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.マリア)'
[endif]
@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.マリア)' cond='game.guest.members.has(o.マリア)'
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@fg c=マリア f=00
[texton]
[マリア v=va218 f=02]「Well, that's it for me. Thanks for your help, everyone.」[k]
[マックス f=11]「Whaaaaat?! You're leaving already?!」[k]
[マリア v=va219 f=02]「I know you guys are going through a lot, but please hang in there. I'll be rooting for you, too.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yeah, thanks. Take care, Maria.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@se f=period
@notice text="<y>Maria left the party."
[eventoff]





;■オークの拠点制圧クエスト

; 洞窟に救ったオークたちを退治するクエスト

;◇イベント・オークの群れと戦闘
*orc_1

; 洞窟内
[texton]
I saw a large group of orcs gathered in a slightly open area at the back of the cave. And in the center of them is [―――]![k]
[textoff]
*_replay_orc_1
@bg f=event92
[texton w=2]
[警備隊長]「Ah... Ah... Stop... Stop...!」[k]
[オーク]「Phew... This is good...!」[k]
Shockingly, the guard captain had been captured by orcs.[k]
She'd been undressed, and was on all fours being raped from behind by one orc.[k]
[警備隊長]「Ugh...! Stop...! Don't... No more humiliation... I won't forgive you... I won't... No!」[k]
[オーク]「Come on, come on, come on. You like this, don't you? Huh? It really feels good, doesn't it?」[k]
∗sluurp!∗[k]
[警備隊長]「I don't... I don't feel good... Aaaaahhh...!」[k]
Penetrated by the orc's thick member, the guard captain couldn't resist making sensual sounds and wiggling her hips.[k]
Seeing this, the orc became even more aroused and began thrusting strongly into her.[k]
[警備隊長]「Ohhh... Ohhh... Stop... Stop it... ahhh..!」[k]
[オーク]「Damn, I can't wait! I'm about to cum! I'm going to cum inside of you again!」[k]
[警備隊長]「Stop it...! I don't want to become pregnant with an orc's child...!」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05
@return cond='f.replayMode'
@gameon
[texton w=0]
To my surprise, the captain of the guard was being used like a sex toy by the orcs.[k]
We can't just leave her like this. We have to help as soon as possible...[k]
[オーク]「What the hell? Are you here to fight us, too?」[k]
Orcs have discovered us. We have no choice but to fight![k]
[オーク]「Hm! Far more of us than them! Let's beat these guys up too!」[k]
[textoff]

; オークの群れと戦闘
@monster pos=0 name=オークソルジャー
@monster pos=1 name=オークソルジャー
@monster pos=2 name=オークソルジャー
@monster pos=3 name=オークソルジャー
@monster pos=4 name=オークソルジャー
@monster pos=5 name=オークソルジャー
@monster pos=6 name=オークソルジャー
@monster pos=7 name=オークシャーマン
@monster pos=8 name=オークシャーマン
@monster pos=9 name=オークシャーマン
@monster pos=10 name=オークシャーマン
@monster pos=11 name=オークシャーマン
@monster pos=12 name=オークシャーマン
@monster pos=13 name=オークシャーマン
@monster pos=15 name=オークキング
@monster pos=16 name=オークキング
@monster pos=17 name=オークキング
@monster pos=18 name=オークキング
@monster pos=19 name=オークキング
@callbattle bgm=boss escape=false gameover=true
; 勝利

@wait time=500
[texton]
After a battle, we managed to fight off the orcs.[k]
[警備隊長 f=04]「...I'm sorry. My squad planned to exterminate them ourselves, but well...」[k]
[警備隊長 f=04]「I don't know what would have happened to us if you guys hadn't come to our rescue. I'm so sorry.」[k]
